# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../main_window.rst:314
msgid "High DPI / 4K Monitors"
msgstr "Visoka DPI / 4K monitori"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../main_window.rst:316
msgid ""
"OpenShot Video Editor provides robust support for High DPI (Dots Per Inch) "
"monitors, ensuring that the interface looks sharp and is easily readable on "
"displays with various DPI settings. This support is particularly beneficial "
"for users with 4K monitors or other high-resolution displays."
msgstr ""
"OpenShot Video Editor pruža snažnu podršku za monitore s visokom DPI "
"(točkama po inču), osiguravajući da su sučelje oštro i lako čitljivo na "
"zaslonima s različitim DPI postavkama. Ova podrška je posebno korisna za "
"korisnike s 4K monitorima ili drugim zaslonima visoke rezolucije."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../main_window.rst:321
msgid "Per Monitor DPI Awareness"
msgstr "Svjesnost DPI-ja po monitoru"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../main_window.rst:323
msgid ""
"OpenShot is DPI aware on a per-monitor basis, meaning it can adjust its "
"scaling dynamically depending on the DPI settings of each connected monitor. "
"This ensures a consistent and high-quality user experience across different "
"displays."
msgstr ""
"OpenShot je svjestan DPI-ja za svaki monitor zasebno, što znači da može "
"dinamički prilagoditi skaliranje ovisno o DPI postavkama svakog povezanog "
"monitora. To osigurava dosljedno i kvalitetno korisničko iskustvo na "
"različitim zaslonima."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../main_window.rst:327
msgid "DPI Scaling on Windows"
msgstr "DPI skaliranje na Windowsu"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../main_window.rst:329
msgid ""
"On Windows, OpenShot rounds the scaling factor to the nearest whole value to "
"maintain visual integrity. This rounding helps avoid visual artifacts in the "
"UI rendering and ensures that the interface elements remain crisp and well-"
"aligned. Due to this rounding, scaling options can sometimes lead to "
"increased font-sizes and a feeling that the UI elements are a bit too large."
msgstr ""
"Na Windowsu, OpenShot zaokružuje faktor skaliranja na najbližu cijelu "
"vrijednost kako bi održao vizualni integritet. Ovo zaokruživanje pomaže "
"izbjeći vizualne artefakte u prikazu sučelja i osigurava da elementi sučelja "
"ostanu oštri i dobro poravnati. Zbog ovog zaokruživanja, opcije skaliranja "
"ponekad mogu dovesti do povećanih veličina fonta i dojma da su elementi "
"sučelja malo preveliki."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../main_window.rst:334
msgid "**125% scaling** rounds to **100%**"
msgstr "**125% skaliranje** se zaokružuje na **100%**"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../main_window.rst:335
msgid "**150% scaling** rounds to **200%**"
msgstr "**150% skaliranje** se zaokružuje na **200%**"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../main_window.rst:338
msgid "Workarounds for Fine-Grained Adjustment"
msgstr "Zaobilazna rješenja za preciznu prilagodbu"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../main_window.rst:340
msgid ""
"While rounding helps maintain a clean interface, there are workarounds for "
"users who require more precise control over the scaling. However, these "
"methods are **not recommended** due to potential visual artifacts:"
msgstr ""
"Iako zaokruživanje pomaže održati čist izgled sučelja, postoje zaobilazna "
"rješenja za korisnike kojima je potrebna preciznija kontrola skaliranja. "
"Međutim, ove metode **nisu preporučene** zbog mogućih vizualnih artefakata:"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../main_window.rst:343
msgid "**QT_SCALE_FACTOR_ROUNDING_POLICY=PassThrough**"
msgstr "**QT_SCALE_FACTOR_ROUNDING_POLICY=PassThrough**"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../main_window.rst:345
msgid ""
"Setting this environment variable can disable rounding and allow more "
"precise scaling."
msgstr ""
"Postavljanje ove varijable okoline može onemogućiti zaokruživanje i "
"omogućiti preciznije skaliranje."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../main_window.rst:346
msgid ""
"**Note:** This may cause visual artifacts, particularly in the timeline, and "
"is not recommended."
msgstr ""
"**Napomena:** Ovo može uzrokovati vizualne artefakte, osobito na vremenskoj "
"crti, i nije preporučeno."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../main_window.rst:348
msgid "**QT_SCALE_FACTOR=1.25** (or similar value)"
msgstr "**QT_SCALE_FACTOR=1.25** (ili slična vrijednost)"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../main_window.rst:350
msgid ""
"Manually setting the scale factor can provide finer adjustments to the font "
"and UI scaling."
msgstr ""
"Ručno postavljanje faktora skaliranja može omogućiti finije prilagodbe "
"veličine fonta i skaliranja sučelja."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../main_window.rst:351
msgid ""
"This can also be set via Preferences (User Interface Scale) - but expect "
"border/line issues on Windows with fractional scales."
msgstr ""
"Ovo se također može postaviti putem Postavki (Skaliranje korisničkog "
"sučelja) - ali očekujte probleme s rubovima/linijama na Windowsu kod "
"decimalnih skaliranja."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../main_window.rst:352
msgid ""
"**Note:** This method can also lead to visual artifacts and make OpenShot "
"harder to use."
msgstr ""
"**Napomena:** Ova metoda također može uzrokovati vizualne artefakte i "
"otežati korištenje OpenShota."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../main_window.rst:354
msgid ""
"For more info on adjusting these environment variables, please visit https://"
"github.com/OpenShot/openshot-qt/wiki/OpenShot-UI-too-large."
msgstr ""
"Za više informacija o podešavanju ovih varijabli okruženja, posjetite "
"https://github.com/OpenShot/openshot-qt/wiki/OpenShot-UI-too-large."
